{"id":295977,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/【图说天朝】堵车堵成麻将牌/","date":"2013-05-30T07:55:26Z","modified":"2013-05-30T07:55:26Z","title":"【图说天朝】堵车堵成麻将牌","content":"<p>5月28日凌晨起，雷雨光顾西安，至13时，过程雨量26.3mm。这是西安在上周末又一场明显降雨，市区积水严重，多处看海，早高峰道路拥堵，雁塔西路和朱雀路交汇处汽车从四方涌，几乎水泄不通，好像人们平时打的麻将。有新浪微博网友称，该处交通指示灯常失灵，可能导致了上述情况。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/162118561836394494481n.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-295978\" alt=\"162118561836394494481n\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/162118561836394494481n.jpg\" width=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/162118561836394494481n.jpg 648w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/162118561836394494481n-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,13770],"tags":[15226,13940,20541]}